graph TD
    A[用户输入] --> B[检测昨天未完成任务]
    B --> C[显示想法停车场]
    C --> D[询问能量状态]
    D --> E[高/中/低]
    E --> F[生成任务提案]
    F --> G[确认任务规格]
    G --> H[创建任务文件夹]
    H --> I[task_plan.md]
    H --> J[progress.md]
    H --> K[findings.md]
    I --> L[展开任务]
    J --> L
    K --> L
    L --> M[执行中...]
    M --> N[实时更新文件]
    N --> M
    M --> O[任务完成]
    O --> P[更新状态]
    P --> Q[归档]

    style A fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style O fill:#9f9,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style H fill:#ff9,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
